Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! She reeks of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:41.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you up on the morning of your day off, Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:44.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.37,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fnRP Mola\b0\be1\bord0.1\shad0\fs70\pos(526,312)\c&H45484E&\3c&H45484E&}Alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.37,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fnRP Mola\b0\be1\bord0.1\shad0\fs70\c&H45484E&\3c&H45484E&\pos(131,437)}Wafting~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:48.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think a day would come when Nomiya\Nwould ask me to do something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:54.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you... just how much did you drink to smell like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For a moment I thought a huge Nara pickle came in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.01,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Nara pickles are pickled in sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.72,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArtificeSSK\fscx65\fsp2\be1\b0\shad2\frz8\fs68\pos(633,195)\c&H765885&\3c&HD4CEF3&}Nara\NPickles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you guys drinking here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:07.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Mayama and his friend were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:11.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They were here... until... a few... minutes... ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya, you seem sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.79,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H64&\3a&H64&\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fs93\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\i1\3c&HBCDCE9&\pos(437,81)\frx14\fry353\c&H6D95D6&\frz16.436}Yamada Liquor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell were you last night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even call!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Yamada-san's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:41.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Teshigawara from Fujiwara Design Office. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:41.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs35\fsp14\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(581,208)\c&H218ED6&}"Hello~"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really must apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:51.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We apparently allowed your daughter to drink a\Nlittle too much at the flower viewing last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some sweet red bean rice that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your generosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've taken good care of my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:07.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, we tried to have her call home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she threw up, collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:08.70,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs70\frz90\shad0\fsp10\move(83,679,83,-229)\3c&HC6D0D3&\c&H000000&}threw up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.71,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs70\frz90\shad0\fsp10\move(83,679,83,-239)\3c&HC6D0D3&\c&H000000&}collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,and then passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.62,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs70\frz90\shad0\fsp10\move(83,679,83,-239)\3c&HC6D0D3&\c&H000000&}passed out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.42,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs70\frz90\shad0\fsp10\move(83,679,83,-239)\3c&HC6D0D3&\c&H000000&}(All the truth)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That must have been a lot of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You good-for-nothing daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, was that passable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was magnificient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the stench sure was powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, how much did she drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:38.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on the ferris wheel, she stank of alcohol...\Neven though the small window was wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.15,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\bord1.5\shad0\fs40\fsp4\frz-75\move(53,300,15,205)\c&H363C44&\3c&HF7FDFF&}Ventillation~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.28,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\bord1.5\shad0\fs40\fsp4\frz75\move(744,296,793,196)\c&H363C44&\3c&HF7FDFF&}I'm sorry~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep. That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:45.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A ferris wheel? That's a rather elegant\Nthing for you to ride on, Nomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:48.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat was saying that you're the type\Nto take her, eat her, and throw her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNew Times Roman\b0\fs44\shad3.2\fsp3\fscx80\be1\3c&H0F191A&\c&H0F191A&\frz-22\bord0.5\pos(774,432)\4c&HF6FFFE&}That\Nbrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNew Times Roman\b0\fs44\shad3.2\fsp3\fscx80\be1\3c&H0F191A&\c&H0F191A&\bord0.5\4c&HF6FFFE&\pos(250,398)\frz26.511}Oh...\Nthat\Nbrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:02.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On that matter... well, let's just say I wasn't\Nable to live up to his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:11.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Being the cushion for a failed love is like pulling the short straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a luxurious cushion she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He crashed just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired out from playing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Miwako-san's bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a wonderful combination!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:42.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This beef sausage and the yellow pickled radishes and this riceball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they good? Miwako-san is the rice-mixing captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second! I'll make you some riceballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Design?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
