Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:03.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this man sure is an interesting creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these clothes custom-made?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:09.28,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Bubble: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Hideki is overwhelmed
