Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the greatest, all right! The greatest in lameness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs35\fsp6\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(146,87)\c&H1C8CD5&}"That's cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:17.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go again, Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}random pun - {\3c&H635514&\be0}"Iku, iku, gyuuniku!" {\be1\3c&H000000&}(Go, go, beef!)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.20,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Bubble: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Time for me to take off my boots and eat breakfast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:47.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez. Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you haven't slept?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the phonecall from Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's gonna drive Yamada-san home\Nand he needs me to take a hit for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like him — to mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to ride the ferris wheel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they were to say that it's just a\Nmisunderstanding, then that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:30.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought to myself... that it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to ride it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been looking at it this whole time,\Nso I thought that you might like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:42.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:45.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:53.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That it was mixed in amongst the vast amount of\Nsample photographs that Nomiya-san had taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he thinking as he closed the shutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:05.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pictures of the ferris wheel that\Nhe took all felt somehow familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is probably... more for looking at from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:19.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a place that was within him this whole time, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:25.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should ask Nomiya-san about it the next time I see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How it felt to ride the ferris wheel for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.60,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(420,293)}I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(428,305)}On T.V. or in magazines,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp2\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(431,247)}love seems fun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(427,362)}land colored with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp2\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(434,305)}But why is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(446,305)}my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(439,305)}so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:00.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1600)\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(439,305)}and despicable?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:24.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when wishing for my happiness is on the opposite\Nside of the coin to wishing for another's misery...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:29.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(418,370)}Then what should I be praying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:32.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morita-san, I heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't actually hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was, seriously worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Why are you always so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one that was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Mayama and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to realize this, so I'll tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an incredibly fortunate person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:58.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two grown men spent an entire night sitting\Ntogether and worrying over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be so irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Morita-san, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you disappeared so inexplicably yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:27.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't even contact us for a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:43.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san kept apologizing and promised me with a straight\Nface that he'd leave a TV-phone the next time he departs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:48.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we held hands as we went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:53.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm unable to pray for myself, I instead prayed\Nto the moon floating in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:58.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the happiness of the person to whom\Nthis warm right hand belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to become a teacher, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it just on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:32.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the people that I lived with in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.15,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\fs30\fscx80\fsp1\b0\fnTimes New Roman\bord1.2\shad0\c&H5B68C8&\3c&H1C353B&\pos(489,27)}Rectus abdominis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:42.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\fs30\fscx80\fsp1\b0\fnTimes New Roman\bord1.2\shad0\c&H5B68C8&\3c&H293740&\pos(633,100)}Rectus abdominis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even thought they could draw and make anything\Nto the point where it ticked me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-kun, what's "rectus abdominis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have it drawn already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:41.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd fail art history or anatomy hopelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:42.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\fs30\fscx80\fsp1\b0\fnTimes New Roman\bord1.2\shad0\c&H5B68C8&\3c&H293740&\pos(184,58)}17th Century\NDutch Style
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:42.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\fs30\fscx80\fsp1\b0\fnTimes New Roman\bord1.2\shad0\c&H5B68C8&\3c&H293740&\pos(318,80)}Mannerism
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:42.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu! What's "mannerism"? What's "17th century Dutch style"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:47.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you raise your arm like this, both\Nyour scapula and clavicle rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And since there are two bones past your elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:57.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have the names of all the bones and muscles in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is he so bad at sketches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-kun, please teach me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two were so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:22.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing their happy faces asking me\Nquestions made the experience fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought to myself, "Ah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've been counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really lifts me up, you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:39.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first enrolled, I was wondering,\N"Why did I ever enter an art school?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody was so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed I was pretty good up 'til then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,so the shock was even greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei says that and laughs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But from my point of view, I think he's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm also very envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:59.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To find people who need you, and to\Ncontinue to answer to their needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's found a place for himself on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About what she's going to do after she graduates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back to the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:28.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll draw everyday, while I tend to the gardens and\Nthe chickens. Just like I did before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:34.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the country, there's plenty of room and\Na dirt floor, so I can make anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:39.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll sometimes have my work displayed\Nat an art gallery that Shuu-chan knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need enough money to buy rice and art materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as long as I can keep drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do want to stay here with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the rent in Tokyo is too high...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:13:00.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I don't want to trouble Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:08.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me realize that even Hagu-chan is thinking\Nabout her future, and it made me feel pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:13.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pineapple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nobody's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you all went out to do something fun without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Korobokkur!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:42.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The one on the right is for the Four Seasons exhibit, and the\None on the left must be for the Marine Light competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:44.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she drawing things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't bad for being an artist in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you make her stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for her to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That she's a person who needs to experience the wider world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People all over the world could meet her at\Nany time if they just go to an art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For a 100 years, or even 300 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's capable of making things that\Nwill keep living, even after she dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:38.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a life where you leave nothing else is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How many females are mentioned in art history texts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And among them, how many of them led a happy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:52.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not be able to leave anything\Nbehind, no matter how much she draws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, she won't be able to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mind may never be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really call that happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your duty to look after her for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:24.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prince isn't the type that would tell\Nme, "Isn't it your duty to look after her?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:37.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A world that I couldn't see, no matter how hard I strained my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams and aspirations that I wasn't able to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:46.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I'm trying to achieve them through Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:52.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... is that really happiness for Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just my ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:16:00.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I honestly say that it's not the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:04.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\i1\b0\shad0\bord0\fs32\frx8\fry12\pos(367,111)\frz332.548\c&H79878D&}Harada Design Office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\i1\b0\shad0\bord0\fs22\frx8\fry12\frz332.548\pos(319,205)\c&H8A97A1&}Representative
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A business card for Harada Design?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sixth floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Harada Design...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:17.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. She made the sixth floor the office and the seventh\Nfloor became exclusively Rika-san's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:26.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, since she's with such a dangerous individual\Nall day long, I've really been worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be burying his face in the bathtowel that Rika-san uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:37.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he's rubbing the edge of the bathtub, saying,\N"Ah... this is where Rika-san must be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:42.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in reality, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I'm a pervert...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\fscy75\b0\shad0\bord0\frx20\fry0\pos(411,185)\frz4.007\c&H879397&}Harada Design Office
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.16,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\b0\shad0\bord0\frz4.486\pos(380,232)\frx22\fry0\c&H8F9BA0&}Representative
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:00.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, was our adolescence this sour?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we call it quits to teasing him soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:06.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he's gonna do something ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, we still have a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:12.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this seriously feels like a punishment game...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:18.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like having my picture album from my student days that\NI don't even want to see anymore just pushed into my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it's like... a rerun of my adolescence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:26.65,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\bord0.1\b0\be1\fnArtificeSSK\fscx50\fsp1\fs53\shad0\c&H011310&\pos(294,441)}Like a rerun of{\c&H02312A&} my ado{\c&H024339&}lesc{\c&H014C40&}ence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:23.07,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}the symbols in the back are the "first-year\Ndriver" bumper stickers for cars in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You had times like that, too, Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when I was adorable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:36.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, while I don't want to admit to it, Mayama and I are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\i1\be1\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fsp1\b0\fs40\move(112,315,109,293)\c&H383933&\3c&HB78527&\frz25.668}Enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\i1\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fsp1\b0\fs40\move(199,102,179,56)\c&H2A2C31&\3c&H9C591F&\frz15.611}Restraint
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\i1\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fsp1\b0\fs40\move(427,173,430,109)\frz15.611\c&H3B3935&\3c&HBB7F1D&}Indecisiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\be1\i1\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\fscx70\fsp1\b0\fs40\move(633,82,615,32)\frz15.211\c&H3B3935&\3c&HBB7F1D&}Pathetic{\frz14.5}ness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:43.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And, as if to spite me, he walks around in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.09,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fscy90\fs35\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\frz10\shad0\bord1\be1\pos(708,138)\c&H5D5952&\3c&HC8C0B7&}Restraint, Regrets,\NEnthusiasm, Indecisiveness,\NPatheticness, Jealousy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:43.09,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\shad0\fscy80\fsp-1\bord0.1\be1\b0\fs54\fnAlsina Ultrajada\c&H1E2D53&\3c&H4D91EF&\pos(244,79)}Escape\NSuccessful
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:48.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing everything that I tried so hard for years to get rid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:48.55,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\fscy90\fs33\fsp-2\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b0\shad0\bord1\be1\3c&HBAB0A4&\frz0.948\pos(503,431)\c&H696256&}Assumption, Adolescence, Mistaken Confidence,\NRegret, Patheticness, Enthusiasm, Jealousy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:48.55,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\bord2\c&H667171&\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fsp1\fscx80\shad0\fs40\pos(745,78)\3c&HD8E2E5&}Suit of\NAdolescence
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:52.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually... can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:56.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently Mayama understands that, and it bothers him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:18:00.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he really hates to make mistakes in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomiya-san is cool, but I have a hard time dealing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:08.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:15.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird to have in front of you a completed\Nform of what you aspire to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\3c&H030101&\fnArtificeSSK\shad0\bord1\be1\fscx70\fsp1\b0\fs36\pos(370,47)\c&H6E8DC3&}O{\c&H6383BE&}d{\c&H597BBA&}e{\c&H5273B7&}n
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he say the cutest things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. A completed form?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:24.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! What completed form?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:28.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.5\shad0\b0\be1\fs23\frz24.538\c&H4B4447&\frx358\fry358\pos(54,40)\3c&HA3847B&}click click
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:28.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing that he can say something like that so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:37.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl prefers the incomplete version...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure makes me lose face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really into your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:19:00.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a break and have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:07.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you must've been really concentrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been hoping for some souvenirs to hand\Nout at the alumni association meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems there's enough for their entire families as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You only needed fourteen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:31.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you can't find the answer, it's the best\Nfor you to just quietly work with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:39.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when you can't find an answer, even if you\Nsit at home and hold your head, or ask others for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:45.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But oddly enough, when you concentrate\Non one task and keep working at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:51.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You may find the answer lying in the\Nhundredth plate that you create.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Work with diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:06.10,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Tub: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Fancy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go work on the remaining fifty-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:06.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my much-valued Shigaraki pottery clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.73,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b0\fs48\fsp5\3c&HEEEFF1&\c&H000308&\shad0\move(1045,305,-94,305)}Shigaraki Pottery Clay
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-kun, my department's budget...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I'm done cleaning up the archive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:17.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:23.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:32.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:41.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What she needs to hear now isn't on the level of\N"What's wrong?" or "I'll listen to your problems."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words won't reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's currently in a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:52.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(428,305)}Dear God
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:21:02.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it more painful to cry when you can't do something you\Nwant to, or when you can't find what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(428,305)}What does "something I want to do" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(428,305)}What do I need to do to find that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(436,305)}Will I become stronger if I can find that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:07.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing that I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(430,305)}Even from her, who is crying so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:10.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That even if I put everything I have into that task...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(428,305)}What I felt was an infinite...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop her tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:18.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1600)\bord0.1\b0\fscx80\fsp3\be1\fs42\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(428,305)}Strength.
